<h3 class="title">Forgot password</h3>
<p>Please, inform the email associated to the account.</p>
<p>If the email is in our database, a link to reset your password will be sent.</p>
<form class="form user-form" method="POST" action="/forgot_password">
  <label for="email">Email:</label>
  <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required><br>

  <button class="submit-button" type="submit" name="submit">Submit</button>
</form>
